{"content": "I need to multiply 512 \u00d7 772 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 512\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 405 + 9 + 2 = 416\u2081\u2080\n- 772\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 567 + 63 + 2 = 632\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 416 \u00d7 632 = 262,912\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 262912 \u00f7 9 = 29212 r 4\n- 29212 \u00f7 9 = 3245 r 7\n- 3245 \u00f7 9 = 360 r 5\n- 360 \u00f7 9 = 40 r 0\n- 40 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 4\n- 4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: **440574\u2089**\n\n440574", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}